Name: Ailin: Traps and Treasures
About the game: Ailin: Traps and Treasures is a block-pushing puzzle game inspired by classics like Sokoban and Minesweeper. Help treasure-hunter Ailin to collect treasures from tombs. Move the treasure chests to extraction points and avoid traps. Detect mines and plan your movements carefully. Create levels and share them with other players. Features 50 various levels Classic block-pushing gameplay New game mechanics Build-in level editor and community levels Controller support
